{"tid":418654,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[今次到三哥了]苗僑偉根本唔適合做正派","createTime":"2017-09-29T17:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T08:24:02.000Z","uid":95418,"like":17,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5edba9e8f8fd52f6e2b2311accf65273fc38f9e2","tid":418654,"uid":95418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:40:29.000Z","msg":"吹完林峯，吹下苗僑偉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n三哥雖然好戲又有型，但佢做正派根本比唔上佢做反派。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由佢做學警出狙擊開始 我覺得佢已經完美演活左考哥呢係位黑社會大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無論佢嘅神情同演技都將考哥變成一位大奸大惡，毫無破綻嘅大佬。之後佢係社團同佢個女之間嘅掙扎位演得淋漓盡致，令觀眾深深感覺得到佢呢位作惡多端嘅大佬都有人性嘅一面。 每集當佢出場已霸氣盡現，攪到啲觀眾都想做埋佢手下。<br />\n之後佢演反派嘅雷霆掃毒，好心作怪同射鵰更加唔洗講佢演得有幾好，直頭搶曬主角啲戲咁。<br />\n反觀最近佢做正派嘅使徒12，集集出黎都搶唔到戲，佢個又嚴苛又冷酷樣完全睇唔出佢有幾緊張啲臥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完美地浪費左三哥嘅演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實明明三哥有曬大boss嘅氣質，點解大台成日要佢做正派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三哥做反派無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你正派不知幾啱佢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc794226f120c62f00208007a94c937442101d9","tid":418654,"uid":2655,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:45:35.000Z","msg":"勿演三鮮凍撚死"},{"pid":"e7a1c24d386cf3b5fdabac4d7076d3594cce458e","tid":418654,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"話晒佢做過楚留香喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf6d746277f3d415bf3d2e5192d52c9af961a34","tid":418654,"uid":78222,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:47:29.000Z","msg":"齊歡唱 你今日贏既機會係零呀 哈哈哈"},{"pid":"a0e78c8d989972294367c52d880604a05fdfef5d","tid":418654,"uid":40804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"媽為什麼不是我想像的那樣.jpg"},{"pid":"fb011daee01c1435606961f0f3a5dc93f2747325","tid":418654,"uid":95418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:53:18.000Z","msg":"佢越老越有大boss味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009fe1f8b887eac75fb5be38c045e7a3746aaf89","tid":418654,"uid":6644,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T18:13:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘩!!!!四條煙呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"795cf93a43a61b362be1340c723158834dd76804","tid":418654,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T18:28:42.000Z","msg":"東邪"},{"pid":"26f2247cbb208575b6e406e7778f0c0a0b8cae61","tid":418654,"uid":39812,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T18:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘩!!!!四條煙呀</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你輸左啦 哈<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">哈</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">哈</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"0b26dc044a0e384c71e81eae5970e509b365276f","tid":418654,"uid":555,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T21:10:30.000Z","msg":"做黃藥師邪得黎少少正氣好睇"},{"pid":"a35abbd6e6ebeb823800a7dfa4b82ce8d6e57f09","tid":418654,"uid":55753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:21:48.000Z","msg":"套劇都未完。話唔定最後又反轉呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b389b2ac4f8451ff0d0abf771c7b529644e382bb","tid":418654,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:42:51.000Z","msg":"腦中浮現好多惡搞圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4f5e2019b9ca84604d215916ad52343e73da7a","tid":418654,"uid":53498,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"佢連演員都無資格啦,咁多年都係零演技,拍得住周驄"},{"pid":"282e5ae100e5301a1a60cde4dd4c85713998e940","tid":418654,"uid":150014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T04:41:25.000Z","msg":"其實佢學警1 做正派好好<br />\n無佢 carry 唱 k 同陳鍵鋒根本唔會變到學警系列<br />\n搞到學警狙擊都要出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15f7816a180e7fc67d8bb73c33ffad1a9233817","tid":418654,"uid":9382,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平行世界入面？"},{"pid":"1dcc103f35d706d898e0e3f1c755fcb09e068bfb","tid":418654,"uid":124450,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"張兆輝係有實力 就算做配角露幾面都可以豐富到套戲嘅context （無可否認都係咁多年嚟杜sir嘅功勞）<br />\n<br />\n三哥做配角（學警狙擊 賭場風雲）就算演技幾雞都好大某程度都同輝哥一樣豐富到套戲 <br />\n<br />\n但係一做主角就仆街 本身角色單薄再加埋佢嘅膠面 ...（可能角色複雜佢未有能力表現出嚟）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輝哥唔同於佢會加啲身體語言落個角色甚至整到一種矛盾感出嚟<br />\n<br />\n廢得嚟又唔係太廢嘅師爺蘇<br />\n柔道龍虎榜 溫溫燉燉但係做嘢專心講嘢狠苦嘅收數大佬 <br />\n保持通話 口多但係個腦精嘅大sir<br />\n全職沒女 冇感情細胞但某啲時候又好浪漫嘅莊富豪<br />\n<br />\n輝哥係創造緊唔同角色出嚟（演員）<br />\n三哥係做緊自己（明星）<br />\n所以輝哥係做唔到主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076693c19e7786ea3f57dbf482e31a36515e9eab","tid":418654,"uid":88126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T10:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張兆輝係有實力 就算做配角露幾面都可以豐富到套戲嘅context （無可否認都係咁多年嚟杜sir嘅功勞）<br />\n<br />\n三哥做配角（學警狙擊 賭場風雲）就算演技幾雞都好大某程度都同輝哥一樣豐富到套戲 <br />\n<br />\n但係一做主角就仆街 本身角色單薄再加埋佢嘅膠面 ...（可能角色複雜佢未有能力表現出嚟）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輝哥唔同於佢會加啲身體語言落個角色甚至整到一種矛盾感出嚟<br />\n<br />\n廢得嚟又唔係太廢嘅師爺蘇<br />\n柔道龍虎榜 溫溫燉燉但係做嘢專心講嘢狠苦嘅收數大佬 <br />\n保持通話 口多但係個腦精嘅大sir<br />\n全職沒女 冇感情細胞但某啲時候又好浪漫嘅莊富豪<br />\n<br />\n輝哥係創造緊唔同角色出嚟（演員）<br />\n三哥係做緊自己（明星）<br />\n所以輝哥係做唔到主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  精僻"},{"pid":"3c230c3c11cc3fb8d4d517c4b0eca51336f1fe5b","tid":418654,"uid":36341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T19:18:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張兆輝係有實力 就算做配角露幾面都可以豐富到套戲嘅context （無可否認都係咁多年嚟杜sir嘅功勞）<br />\n<br />\n三哥做配角（學警狙擊 賭場風雲）就算演技幾雞都好大某程度都同輝哥一樣豐富到套戲 <br />\n<br />\n但係一做主角就仆街 本身角色單薄再加埋佢嘅膠面 ...（可能角色複雜佢未有能力表現出嚟）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輝哥唔同於佢會加啲身體語言落個角色甚至整到一種矛盾感出嚟<br />\n<br />\n廢得嚟又唔係太廢嘅師爺蘇<br />\n柔道龍虎榜 溫溫燉燉但係做嘢專心講嘢狠苦嘅收數大佬 <br />\n保持通話 口多但係個腦精嘅大sir<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全職沒女 冇感情細胞但某啲時候又好浪漫嘅莊富豪</span><br />\n<br />\n輝哥係創造緊唔同角色出嚟（演員）<br />\n三哥係做緊<span style=\"color: red;\">自己（明星）<br />\n所以輝哥係做唔到主角</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0f18bfb4d89111b9c3710de72e27da83715743d9","tid":418654,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T19:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>張兆輝係有實力 就算做配角露幾面都可以豐富到套戲嘅context （無可否認都係咁多年嚟杜sir嘅功勞）<br />\n<br />\n三哥做配角（學警狙擊 賭場風雲）就算演技幾雞都好大某程度都同輝哥一樣豐富到套戲 <br />\n<br />\n但係一做主角就仆街 本身角色單薄再加埋佢嘅膠面 ...（可能角色複雜佢未有能力表現出嚟）<br />\